<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>عُمَرَ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>٢٧ -<span class="c5"> وَسَأَلْتُهُ عَنْ قَوْلِ النَّاسِ فِي الْبَرَاغِيثِ:</span> <span class="c1">"أَنَّ النَّبِيَّ <span class="c2">(صَلَّى اللَّهُ عَلَيْهِ وَسَلَّمَ)</span> دَعَا لَهَا"</span>، أَتَعْرِفُهُ فِي شَيْءٍ مِنَ الْحَدِيثِ؟.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">قَالَ:</span> لا! وعجب من قولي له!!<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>